    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I've been using this to bubble up custom errors:\r\n\r\n```\r\n    try contract.externalCall(data) {\r\n        // on success\r\n        } catch (bytes memory reason) {\r\n            // on revert\r\n            assembly {\r\n                revert(add(32, reason), mload(reason))\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n```",
